By bumping up to level 8 on 2.15 we have these initial issues on the on other branches as it was only added there in the upstream merge. Since I didn't fixed all the issues on the upstreams during merging I'm happy @julienfalque made these PRs :)

After these, I expect way less issues as now all PR's will be tested with the new level 8.
We might hit a conflict on the baseline every now and than, but it is a small price to pay compared to what it bring us IMHO.

